    <p>Team Peter & Edita help Titirangi homeowners prepare, position and market their homes with a clear seller strategy. That includes honest pricing advice, professional presentation guidance, buyer-focused marketing, AI-enhanced buyer targeting, careful follow-up and negotiation support.</p>

    <p>Every property has a different buyer story. Some homes need lifestyle positioning. Some need buyer confidence around documents or maintenance. Some need stronger presentation. Some need better targeting to reach the right buyer group.</p>

    <p>If you are thinking about selling in Titirangi, the best first step is to understand how buyers will see your property before it goes live.</p>

